; Regression test for issue #707: Year directive confuses today for entry command (BZ#707)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/707
;
; When a 'year' directive sets a different year in the journal, the 'entry'
; command should still use the actual current date (--now), not a date from
; the year directive's year.

year 2010

01/01 Test Transaction
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test --now 2012/03/25 entry "Test Transaction"
2012/03/25 Test Transaction
    Expenses:Food                             $10.00
    Assets:Cash
end test

test --now 2012/03/25 entry thursday "Test Transaction"
2012/03/22 Test Transaction
    Expenses:Food                             $10.00
    Assets:Cash
end test

; Partial date (month/day only) should use --now year, not year directive
test --now 2012/03/25 xact 03/20 "Test Transaction"
2012/03/20 Test Transaction
    Expenses:Food                             $10.00
    Assets:Cash
end test
